    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated or formally scoped. Seven factors were assessed and all show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5, confirming the Not Accepted submission decision. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. The assessment is accepted as complete and ready for regulatory submission with the explicit Not Accepted finding. The hemolysis model selection methodology is anchored to the power-law coefficient framework described in the literature (doi:10.1016/j.ymeth.2024.03.003); this reference is cited in the model form factor rationale but does not resolve to a typed node within this package graph.",
